Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊澤洛斯竟然受到了MS的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不經任何勸告就發動突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎敵方的MS中還混有新型機體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯  那些傢伙可是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普勞德的援救作戰計劃還是改期吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（普勞德：聯邦殖民衛星）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  更要快馬加鞭才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這關係到眾多同志的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能失去他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來聯絡救援部隊  轉告他們作戰變更事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:15.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#01  天使再臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們聯邦政府為了消滅反政府勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直隸於政府的治安維持部隊即日起開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治安維持部隊與聯邦保安局緊密聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行高效作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才司令部對我下達了轉屬至獨立治安維持部隊的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親眼見見傳說中的A-LAWS也不壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個部隊的秘密太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如能把內情告訴我就好辦多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正有此意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是馬內金上校打來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼急事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  那件事你考慮過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必這麼快做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（拉格朗日4  殖民衛星普勞德）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  繼續  繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越來越能幹了哦  新人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到這裡已經半年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再新人新人地叫我  可以稱呼我沙慈·克洛斯羅德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是艾迪·宮坂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人懷疑你與卡塔隆勾結…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（卡塔隆：反聯邦政府組織）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮坂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這是做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟我們一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們究竟做錯什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的新造航空巡洋艦  正轉變方向前往拉格朗日4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如王留美所報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會駕駛Seravee出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Seravee Gundam：GN-008 熾天使高達，Virtue的強化機型）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如果還活著  就一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:25.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}（殖民衛星普勞德  高重力工業區劃）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在如此高重力下  居然連機器都不能用…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別停手  R81
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  想活命就閉上嘴好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去工作  R81
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離普勞德還有2300
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子散佈  維持通常濃度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑江中校似乎找到卡塔隆艦艇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  偵查部隊捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始傳送掃描圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是準備前往普勞德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型自動機器人狀態怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部機體可以行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開對反政府勢力的掃蕩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD第一小隊  準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:36.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（AHEAD：先鋒，A-LAWS新型機）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD第一小隊  準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD  自動機器人搭載容器連接完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機無異常  ALL GREEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基寧上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機的哈萊維準尉是初次作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她感受下戰場的氣氛就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基寧小隊出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這裡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能為了這麼點小事就認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在宇宙  總有一天能見到路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你不像是軍人  你也是卡塔隆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是被捲進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你交好運了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪算好運？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點準備待機  馬上開始作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰計劃是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我們只是接到了待機命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼扔下我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Realdo部隊  完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Realdo：原Union舊型機體）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  開始進行救援作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對第7區進行重力系統干預
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始干預
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了  同伴來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長  在正上方發現MS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉加中尉  突入敵方部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萊維準尉原地待機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按原定計劃進行新型自動機器人性能實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載容器分離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型自動機器人開始運行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對人的自動機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對人兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS做的好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道是…刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======================================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:11:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的走狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機  判斷得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  為什麼你會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時候起  一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E Sensor上有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人增援來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我追求的…才不是這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩也是  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上頭盔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉  那個機影是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那種GN粒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動機器人的數量  在減少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉  上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  EXIA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam EXIA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  為什麼你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何到這時候還要出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞  只是在破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這種事的你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來驅逐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是Gundam  也是五年前的機體了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是AHEAD的對手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機  快掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  哈萊維準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我們上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多同伴都是被你們幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此討還！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的時代  已經過去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從背後長出臉來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退  哈萊維準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  三號機！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在打探A-LAWS的行動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了  刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞·埃德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德先生找到EXIA了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  你果然在普勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王小姐的情報好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會嚇一跳的  見到拉塞你之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著啊  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就能裝上EXIA的太陽爐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普勞德出現了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得感謝他們才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了他們  才能救出倖存下來的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能會成為武力介入的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是和我們志同道合的人  席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年不見  你變了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是一點沒變  還跟以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台Gundam  是Celestial Being的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在駕駛Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說  五年前的武力介入也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎  因為你們的所為  很多人死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的人受到傷害…家人和親戚被殺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…失去了唯一的親人姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為跟Celestial Being扯上關係  就被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲也是…姐姐也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不在了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說句話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她們兩個還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會遭到Gundam的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來  我們就更有存在的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種人會進入A-LAWS裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲·哈萊維  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此你也有理由戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲  人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立治安維持部隊和新的Gundam進行了接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於其是否隸屬Celestial Being還尚未確認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府對此事態…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為處女座的我  從未如此地高興過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍獨立治安維持部隊來迎接蘇摩·佩麗絲中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第五MS中隊所屬  安德烈·斯米爾諾夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候加入了A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有回答你的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  不  謝爾蓋·斯米爾諾夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…親？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:06.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:11.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:18.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:27.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:31.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:39.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:49.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:55.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:22:00.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:07.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:12.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:17.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:19.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:23.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:28.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:06.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛說愛「過於沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:11.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉變成恨之前　把它拒絕於心門之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:18.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把不合時宜的事隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是冒牌貨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫時代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:27.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本應定下約定的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:31.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毫無察覺地擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:39.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始崩壞但曾經互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的末路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:49.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:55.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要從當初墮落的印象中逃離開去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:22:00.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算歷經千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:07.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙眸　你手中的余溫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:12.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小聲嘟囔著「愛總是讓我遍體鱗傷…」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:17.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏懼堅信不疑的事而哭過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:19.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道軟弱才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:23.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕堅信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:28.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是愛的真諦吧
